				<td colspan="2"><span>You can use FM on the fly... I use it running around corners
<br />
the most.
<br />

<br />
I haven't seen a limit to the duration of the invis.  It lasts
<br />
consistantly long.  You can move around and it wont break.
<br />
If you had a song playing when you hit FM you will be invis
<br />
with the song still playing. Kinda nice with selo's playing.
<br />

<br />
It does not make you invis to undead.  If something can see
<br />
invis it will see you with FM.  So you can easily reagro.
<br />

<br />
I can actually fade right next to a mob and deagro it without
<br />
worry.  However if a caster had started a nuke for you and
<br />
you FM it will break your invis afterwards and if they were KoS
<br />
to you, they will reagro.
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
